english.local_text:
Glory, Glory in the Highest;
Glory to the Almighty
Glory to the Lamb of God, and
Glory to the living Word;
Glory to the Lamb!

 CHORUS:
(Men) I give Glory (Women) glory;
(Men) Glory (Women) glory,
(All) Glory, glory to the Lamb
I give glory to the Lamb!)

Jesus, Name above all Names
Beautiful Saviour, Glorious Lord;
Emmanuel, God is with us;
Blessed Redeemer, Living Word.

Our God is an awesome God;
He reigns from heaven above
with wisdom, pow’r, and love;
Our God is an awesome God!

Such love pure as the whitest snow
 such love Weeps for the shame I know;
Such love paying the debt I owe;
 O Jesus such love.

2.Such love,stilling my restlessness
Such love filling my emptiness
Such love,showing me holiness;
O Jesus,such love

3.Such love,springs from eternity; such love
Streaming through history
Such love fountain of the to me;
O Jesus,such love
